{"tid":2107801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞氏保加症男童認向警察宿舍掟汽油彈 官欲研究英案例始判刑","createTime":"2020-07-14T06:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T01:38:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":91,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a9ff8d586e5c2569745a541753096f49632877","tid":2107801,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/HVGQOZPYW5FTZGSXIHHG2K5SJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FHVGQOZPYW5FTZGSXIHHG2K5SJU%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=121bbbc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FHVGQOZPYW5FTZGSXIHHG2K5SJU%2F&h=5315ed99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/HVGQOZPYW5FTZGSXIHHG2K5SJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年11月抗爭者死守理大校園苦戰期間，患有亞氏保加症的16歲中四男童向柴灣已婚警察宿舍掟汽油彈，遭目擊事件的途人制服。男童早前在東區裁判法院少年法庭承認罔顧生命是否會受到危害而縱火罪，控方早前確認事件中無人受傷，裁判官何俊堯則謂：「唯一受傷可能係被告被制服嘅時候。」何官今要求控辯雙方就英國去年發出的判刑指引是否適用於本案作出書面陳詞，並索取進一步感化報告。案件押後至7月31日始判刑，男童獲准繼續保釋。"},{"pid":"b26a41535cfe2171b6f190d107603cdf9f39d46f","tid":2107801,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":162,"score":-146,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"弱智都恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aec0e9033f39a783c9dfa3679beed550cbd877","tid":2107801,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c49b7959e9f40f0c8c81ac9b9b327c370f7107","tid":2107801,"uid":226955,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"quote":{"pid":"b26a41535cfe2171b6f190d107603cd